'''''Leyen Spiegel''''' is a two-volume book of sermons, with parallel texts in Estonian and German. It was written by [[Heinrich Stahl]] and published in [[Tallinn]] in 1641 and 1649.<ref>[http://www.utlib.ee/ekollekt/eeva/index.php?do=tekst_yldandmed&lang=4&tid=1078 Tartu University Digital text repository]</ref> It is one of the oldest complete Estonian language books to survive. An original copy is held in the [[National Library of Estonia]].

